00:34:38,199 --> 00:34:39,880
[SPEAKER_00] Kao što je to

664
00:34:39,880 --> 00:34:40,760
[SPEAKER_00] ta ista zona

665
00:34:40,760 --> 00:34:42,119
[SPEAKER_00] za osobu u 25 godina

666
00:34:42,119 --> 00:34:43,219
[SPEAKER_00] možda 12 km

667
00:34:43,219 --> 00:34:44,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili 15 km na sat,

668
00:34:44,420 --> 00:34:46,199
[SPEAKER_00] ovisi u kakvoj formi.

669
00:34:46,199 --> 00:34:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] Ali važno je

670
00:34:48,119 --> 00:34:48,940
[SPEAKER_00] biti dovoljno jak,

671
00:34:48,940 --> 00:34:50,079
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo jak,

672
00:34:50,079 --> 00:34:51,460
[SPEAKER_00] nego kontrolirati svoje tijelo

673
00:34:51,460 --> 00:34:54,239
[SPEAKER_00] čak pri malo većim brzinama.

674
00:34:54,239 --> 00:34:55,940
[SPEAKER_00] Što opet zvuči kao nešto

675
00:34:55,940 --> 00:34:56,639
[SPEAKER_00] jako teško,

676
00:34:56,639 --> 00:34:57,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali nije.

677
00:34:57,059 --> 00:34:58,320
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, poruka.

678
00:34:58,320 --> 00:35:00,079
[SPEAKER_00] Skleknaj na ruci nije ništa strašno,

679
00:35:01,199 --> 00:35:02,199
[SPEAKER_00] jer ti nisam opisao

680
00:35:02,199 --> 00:35:02,940
[SPEAKER_00] do kraja vježbu.

681
00:35:02,940 --> 00:35:04,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ne mora biti na podu,

682
00:35:04,199 --> 00:35:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] neka bude na stolu

683
00:35:05,119 --> 00:35:05,480
[SPEAKER_00] i evo,

684
00:35:05,480 --> 00:35:07,139
[SPEAKER_00] to je test za sve naše gledatelje.

685
00:35:07,139 --> 00:35:08,880
[SPEAKER_00] Ruka na stolu,

686
00:35:08,880 --> 00:35:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] noge na podu.

687
00:35:09,579 --> 00:35:10,619
[SPEAKER_00] Da vidimo koliko nisko

688
00:35:10,619 --> 00:35:11,719
[SPEAKER_00] možeš doći

689
00:35:11,719 --> 00:35:12,420
[SPEAKER_00] na jednoj ruci.

690
00:35:12,420 --> 00:35:13,519
[SPEAKER_00] Ako ti je pre teško,

691
00:35:13,519 --> 00:35:14,699
[SPEAKER_00] kreni sa zidom

692
00:35:14,699 --> 00:35:16,300
[SPEAKER_00] i to dlano visini ramena.

693
00:35:16,300 --> 00:35:17,599
[SPEAKER_00] Pa za godinu dana

694
00:35:17,599 --> 00:35:18,440
[SPEAKER_00] dođi do dlana

695
00:35:18,440 --> 00:35:19,800
[SPEAKER_00] na stolu.

696
00:35:19,800 --> 00:35:20,739
[SPEAKER_00] To je fenomenalna naprava.

697
00:35:20,739 --> 00:35:22,340
[SPEAKER_01] onda možemo i na podu.

698
00:35:22,340 --> 00:35:22,940
[SPEAKER_00] O tom podu.

699
00:35:22,940 --> 00:35:23,900
[SPEAKER_00] Ko može na podu,

700
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,159
[SPEAKER_00] taj možda i ne mora to raditi.

701
00:35:25,159 --> 00:35:26,139
[SPEAKER_01] Ajde, javite nam se,

702
00:35:26,139 --> 00:35:26,820
[SPEAKER_01] svi molim vas,

703
00:35:26,820 --> 00:35:27,519
[SPEAKER_01] u komentare

704
00:35:27,519 --> 00:35:28,619
[SPEAKER_01] koji možete na podu,

705
00:35:28,619 --> 00:35:30,139
[SPEAKER_01] a za sve nas ostalo

706
00:35:30,139 --> 00:35:31,199
[SPEAKER_01] krenit ćemo od zida.

707
00:35:31,199 --> 00:35:32,639
[SPEAKER_00] bit će i koji mogu na podu.

708
00:35:32,639 --> 00:35:33,519
[SPEAKER_01] Sigurno.

709
00:35:33,519 --> 00:35:36,280
[SPEAKER_01] Jakost i izdržljivost.

710
00:35:36,280 --> 00:35:36,599
[SPEAKER_00] Tako je.

711
00:35:36,599 --> 00:35:37,480
[SPEAKER_00] Sad ta izdržljivost

712
00:35:37,480 --> 00:35:38,739
[SPEAKER_00] opet se gradira.

713
00:35:38,739 --> 00:35:40,800
[SPEAKER_00] Za osobu koja je možda

714
00:35:40,800 --> 00:35:41,920
[SPEAKER_00] mlađe životne dobi

715
00:35:41,920 --> 00:35:43,239
[SPEAKER_00] je to nešto drugo.

716
00:35:43,239 --> 00:35:43,940
[SPEAKER_00] Ali ono što je bitno

717
00:35:43,940 --> 00:35:45,039
[SPEAKER_00] da provedeš vrijeme,

718
00:35:45,039 --> 00:35:45,559
[SPEAKER_00] rekao sam mu,

719
00:35:45,559 --> 00:35:46,179
[SPEAKER_00] nisko intenzivno.

720
00:35:46,179 --> 00:35:47,480
[SPEAKER_00] Kakav je to nisko intenzivni trening?

721
00:35:47,480 --> 00:35:48,019
[SPEAKER_00] Pa to je recimo

722
00:35:48,019 --> 00:35:49,920
[SPEAKER_00] da možeš skoro normalno pjevat

723
00:35:49,920 --> 00:35:51,440
[SPEAKER_00] i lagano trčat

724
00:35:51,440 --> 00:35:52,539
[SPEAKER_00] ili biciklirat.

725
00:35:52,539 --> 00:35:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] To ti je zona dva,

726
00:35:53,380 --> 00:35:54,460
[SPEAKER_00] popularna zona dva

727
00:35:54,460 --> 00:35:56,820
[SPEAKER_00] o kojoj ste vjerojatno čuli puno.

728
00:35:56,920 --> 00:35:59,099
[SPEAKER_00] Zona dva je za većinu ljudi

729
00:35:59,099 --> 00:36:01,039
[SPEAKER_00] najlakši mogući jogging.

730
00:36:01,039 --> 00:36:03,360
[SPEAKER_00] Ne moraš biti pogačar

731
00:36:03,360 --> 00:36:04,599
[SPEAKER_00] najbolji biciklist

732
00:36:04,599 --> 00:36:05,460
[SPEAKER_00] kojim je zona dva

733
00:36:05,460 --> 00:36:08,340
[SPEAKER_00] kad vrti na 320 wati bicikl.

734
00:36:08,340 --> 00:36:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] A obična osoba

735
00:36:09,579 --> 00:36:10,840
[SPEAKER_00] kad vrti na 150 wati

736
00:36:10,840 --> 00:36:11,340
[SPEAKER_00] je u šoku.

737
00:36:11,340 --> 00:36:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, on je na 320 wati

738
00:36:14,039 --> 00:36:15,500
[SPEAKER_00] i 4 sata provede u toj zoni.

739
00:36:15,500 --> 00:36:17,300
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, zona dva je nešto

740
00:36:17,300 --> 00:36:19,400
[SPEAKER_00] je zona u kojoj možeš dugo biti.

741
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] I ne trošite.

742
00:36:20,900 --> 00:36:22,079
[SPEAKER_00] Za moje sportaše,

743
00:36:22,079 --> 00:36:23,139
[SPEAKER_00] za moje neke igrače

744
00:36:23,139 --> 00:36:25,739
[SPEAKER_00] zona dva je 12 ili 13 km na sat.

745
00:36:25,739 --> 00:36:26,679
[SPEAKER_00] To je njima zona dva.

746
00:36:26,920 --> 00:36:28,039
[SPEAKER_00] Što je fenomenalno.

747
00:36:28,039 --> 00:36:29,179
[SPEAKER_00] Ali naravno,

748
00:36:29,179 --> 00:36:32,139
[SPEAKER_00] civilu je to možda ubrzani hod.

749
00:36:32,139 --> 00:36:33,800
[SPEAKER_00] Što je isto tako

750
00:36:33,800 --> 00:36:34,579
[SPEAKER_00] dosta dobra stvar.

751
00:36:34,579 --> 00:36:35,480
[SPEAKER_00] Da ne ulazimo sad

752
00:36:35,480 --> 00:36:36,400
[SPEAKER_00] koliko je to laktata,

753
00:36:36,400 --> 00:36:37,059
[SPEAKER_00] to sad nije bitno.

754
00:36:37,059 --> 00:36:37,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da možeš skoro

755
00:36:37,780 --> 00:36:38,460
[SPEAKER_00] normalno pjevat

756
00:36:38,460 --> 00:36:39,820
[SPEAKER_00] i time se baviti.

757
00:36:39,820 --> 00:36:40,639
[SPEAKER_00] Čime se baviš.

758
00:36:40,639 --> 00:36:41,840
[SPEAKER_00] Ako više ne možeš

759
00:36:41,840 --> 00:36:42,420
[SPEAKER_00] normalno pjevat,

760
00:36:42,420 --> 00:36:43,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali i dalje pričaš

761
00:36:43,139 --> 00:36:43,760
[SPEAKER_00] u rečenicama,

762
00:36:43,760 --> 00:36:45,360
[SPEAKER_00] onda si i dalje

763
00:36:45,360 --> 00:36:46,219
[SPEAKER_00] u aerobnoj zoni,

764
00:36:46,219 --> 00:36:48,460
[SPEAKER_00] ali si već u malo višoj

765
00:36:48,460 --> 00:36:49,340
[SPEAKER_00] aerobnoj zoni.

766
00:36:49,340 --> 00:36:50,579
[SPEAKER_00] I isto tako bilo bi dobro

767
00:36:50,579 --> 00:36:51,739
[SPEAKER_00] jednom ili dva puta tjedno

768
00:36:51,739 --> 00:36:52,719
[SPEAKER_00] provesti neko vrijeme

769
00:36:52,719 --> 00:36:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] u toj zoni.

770
00:36:53,380 --> 00:36:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] Preporuke koje su

771
00:36:55,099 --> 00:36:56,179
[SPEAKER_00] preporuke najvećih

772
00:36:56,179 --> 00:36:57,099
[SPEAKER_00] svjetskih zdravstvenih

773
00:36:57,099 --> 00:36:58,039
[SPEAKER_00] organizacija su

774
00:36:58,039 --> 00:37:00,280
[SPEAKER_00] da si tjelesno aktivan

775
00:37:00,280 --> 00:37:01,519
[SPEAKER_00] i čak da tjelesno vježbaš

776
00:37:01,519 --> 00:37:02,920
[SPEAKER_00] oko 150 minuta tjedno.

777
00:37:02,920 --> 00:37:05,119
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, pet puta po 30 minuta

778
00:37:05,119 --> 00:37:07,019
[SPEAKER_00] neke vrste aerobne aktivnosti

779
00:37:07,019 --> 00:37:08,500
[SPEAKER_00] koja ne mora biti čak čisto aerobna,

780
00:37:08,500 --> 00:37:09,980
[SPEAKER_00] može biti malo intenzivniji od toga.

781
00:37:09,980 --> 00:37:12,159
[SPEAKER_00] Dakle, neke niske, srednje

782
00:37:12,159 --> 00:37:12,880
[SPEAKER_00] pa do visoke,

783
00:37:12,880 --> 00:37:15,079
[SPEAKER_00] visoko intenzivne tjelesne aktivnosti

784
00:37:15,079 --> 00:37:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] odnosno vježbanja.

785
00:37:15,800 --> 00:37:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] To su neke preporuke.

786
00:37:17,239 --> 00:37:18,300
[SPEAKER_00] Što može zvući puno,

787
00:37:18,300 --> 00:37:19,840
[SPEAKER_00] pet puta tjedno po 30 minuta,

788
00:37:19,940 --> 00:37:20,880
[SPEAKER_00] ne mora biti možda toliko.

789
00:37:20,880 --> 00:37:22,199
[SPEAKER_00] Ali jednom tjedno

790
00:37:22,199 --> 00:37:23,159
[SPEAKER_00] ili dva puta tjedno

791
00:37:23,159 --> 00:37:24,800
[SPEAKER_00] digni frekvenciju srca

792
00:37:24,800 --> 00:37:26,940
[SPEAKER_00] u zonu da ti je blago neugodno

793
00:37:26,940 --> 00:37:28,400
[SPEAKER_00] ili neudobno, bolje reći.

794
00:37:28,400 --> 00:37:30,239
[SPEAKER_00] U zonu koja je

795
00:37:30,239 --> 00:37:31,699
[SPEAKER_00] van zone konfora

796
00:37:31,699 --> 00:37:32,500
[SPEAKER_00] i gdje se osjećaš

797
00:37:32,500 --> 00:37:34,000
[SPEAKER_00] da ti je zaista intenzivno.

798
00:37:34,000 --> 00:37:35,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jednom ili dva puta tjedno.

799
00:37:35,139 --> 00:37:35,719
[SPEAKER_00] Koliko dugo?

800
00:37:35,719 --> 00:37:38,519
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ako si osoba neke srednje dobi

801
00:37:38,519 --> 00:37:41,420
[SPEAKER_00] ili tamo iza one gospodine.

802
00:37:41,420 --> 00:37:42,719
[SPEAKER_00] Iza mene je bila osoba srednje.

803
00:37:42,719 --> 00:37:45,139
[SPEAKER_00] Ili mlađe,

804
00:37:45,139 --> 00:37:46,579
[SPEAKER_00] onda je to jednom ili dva puta tjedno

805
00:37:46,579 --> 00:37:48,119
[SPEAKER_00] po recimo 10-15 minuta

806
00:37:48,119 --> 00:37:50,300
[SPEAKER_00] visoko intenzivne aktivnosti.

807
00:37:50,300 --> 00:37:52,019
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bila neka zona iznad.

808
00:37:52,019 --> 00:37:52,880
[SPEAKER_00] Iznad, naravno.

809
00:37:52,880 --> 00:37:54,619
[SPEAKER_00] Zona dva je nešto što bi svaki dan

810
00:37:54,619 --> 00:37:55,119
[SPEAKER_00] trebali imati.

811
00:37:55,119 --> 00:37:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] To je higijena.

812
00:37:55,780 --> 00:37:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] A onda jednom ili dva puta tjedno

813
00:37:57,840 --> 00:37:59,440
[SPEAKER_00] da ulaziš u zone 4 ili 5

814
00:37:59,440 --> 00:38:01,360
[SPEAKER_00] da malo pređeš na nerobni prag.

815
00:38:01,360 --> 00:38:02,320
[SPEAKER_00] A to znači da već

816
00:38:02,320 --> 00:38:03,159
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš pričati

817
00:38:03,159 --> 00:38:04,179
[SPEAKER_00] u normalnim rečenicama,

818
00:38:04,179 --> 00:38:06,599
[SPEAKER_00] ne možeš bez da se o to osjeti

819
00:38:06,599 --> 00:38:08,599
[SPEAKER_00] po pitanju tvoje frekvencije disanja.

820
00:38:08,599 --> 00:38:09,679
[SPEAKER_00] Da kad preko telefona

821
00:38:09,679 --> 00:38:10,239
[SPEAKER_00] pričaš nekim

822
00:38:10,239 --> 00:38:11,239
[SPEAKER_00] da o taj neko zaista

823
00:38:11,239 --> 00:38:12,940
[SPEAKER_00] vidi da ti ozbiljno treniraš.

824
00:38:13,280 --> 00:38:14,000
[SPEAKER_00] Ova zona dva je

825
00:38:14,000 --> 00:38:15,639
[SPEAKER_00] da netko nije siguran

826
00:38:15,639 --> 00:38:16,780
[SPEAKER_00] jesi li ti u treningu

827
00:38:16,780 --> 00:38:17,239
[SPEAKER_00] ili nisi.

828
00:38:17,239 --> 00:38:20,360
[SPEAKER_01] I da pričaš preko telefona.

829
00:38:20,360 --> 00:38:21,460
[SPEAKER_01] I pričaš preko telefona

830
00:38:21,460 --> 00:38:22,699
[SPEAKER_01] je tamman si se izviko

831
00:38:22,699 --> 00:38:23,199
[SPEAKER_01] na djecu.

832
00:38:23,199 --> 00:38:25,000
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš malo povišen puls

833
00:38:25,000 --> 00:38:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] i izvučiš kod da si zapravo

834
00:38:26,300 --> 00:38:27,639
[SPEAKER_01] i šume došla sa zone 2.

835
00:38:27,639 --> 00:38:28,280
[SPEAKER_01] Recimo da.

836
00:38:28,280 --> 00:38:31,420
[SPEAKER_01] Dakle, sve što trebamo je zapravo

837
00:38:31,420 --> 00:38:33,199
[SPEAKER_01] pokušat pjevat

838
00:38:33,199 --> 00:38:34,880
[SPEAKER_01] dok šetamo intenzivnije

839
00:38:34,880 --> 00:38:35,920
[SPEAKER_01] malo po kvartu,

840
00:38:35,920 --> 00:38:37,420
[SPEAKER_01] po ulici, po naselju.

841
00:38:37,420 --> 00:38:40,239
[SPEAKER_01] To raditi minimalno 30 minuta

842
00:38:40,239 --> 00:38:40,960
[SPEAKER_01] svaki dan

843
00:38:40,960 --> 00:38:43,539
[SPEAKER_01] ukoliko imamo priliku.

844
00:38:43,539 --> 00:38:45,639
[SPEAKER_01] To bi bilo zapravo optimalno.

845
00:38:45,639 --> 00:38:46,780
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo reći.

846
00:38:46,780 --> 00:38:47,880
[SPEAKER_01] I dva puta tjedno

847
00:38:47,880 --> 00:38:49,980
[SPEAKER_01] dovese u zonu iznad toga

848
00:38:49,980 --> 00:38:51,340
[SPEAKER_01] gdje što s godinama

849
00:38:51,340 --> 00:38:52,579
[SPEAKER_01] bi trebali malo produljiti

850
00:38:52,579 --> 00:38:53,500
[SPEAKER_01] trajanje te zone

851
00:38:53,500 --> 00:38:54,659
[SPEAKER_01] ako sam te dobro shvatila.

852
00:38:55,000 --> 00:38:56,619
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, trebali bi produljiti

853
00:38:56,619 --> 00:38:58,159
[SPEAKER_00] ovo zonu, zonu 2 bi trebalo.

854
00:38:58,159 --> 00:39:00,539
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim, zona 2 je svima potrebna.

855
00:39:00,539 --> 00:39:02,099
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da, ovo pjevanje je da.

856
00:39:02,099 --> 00:39:03,719
[SPEAKER_00] Ako će vas neko čudno gledat

857
00:39:03,719 --> 00:39:04,659
[SPEAKER_00] staviti slušalice,

858
00:39:04,659 --> 00:39:06,920
[SPEAKER_00] pa ćeš gledat kao da je to normalno.

859
00:39:06,920 --> 00:39:07,679
[SPEAKER_01] Pa će vas malo manje, manje da.

860
00:39:07,679 --> 00:39:09,460
[SPEAKER_01] To ono kad glaši neko priča sam sa sobom

861
00:39:09,460 --> 00:39:10,539
[SPEAKER_01] odmah glaši ili ima slušalice.

862
00:39:10,539 --> 00:39:12,659
[SPEAKER_00] Samo tako je, stavi slušalicu i sve u reći.

863
00:39:12,659 --> 00:39:13,599
[SPEAKER_01] I sve, i sve, ok.

864
00:39:13,599 --> 00:39:16,360
[SPEAKER_01] Možeš maskirati svoje demone u glavi

865
00:39:16,360 --> 00:39:18,139
[SPEAKER_01] koji su se pojavili u tom trenutku.

866
00:39:18,139 --> 00:39:21,800
[SPEAKER_01] Postoji li ipak neko vrijeme

867
00:39:21,800 --> 00:39:24,119
[SPEAKER_01] kad je kasno započet sa svim tim stvarima?

868
00:39:24,119 --> 00:39:27,679
[SPEAKER_01] Da li ono kao, evo, imam sad 85 godina,

869
00:39:27,679 --> 00:39:30,119
[SPEAKER_01] možda stvarno bi bilo onda zdravije nastave

870
00:39:30,119 --> 00:39:31,239
[SPEAKER_01] živjeti kako si je živio,

871
00:39:31,239 --> 00:39:32,760
[SPEAKER_01] nego iću nekakav stres

872
00:39:32,760 --> 00:39:35,239
[SPEAKER_01] po pitanju uvođenja nekakve tjelesne aktivnosti?

