1070
00:45:46,079 --> 00:45:48,820
[SPEAKER_00] To je zašto koji je univerzalan.

1071
00:45:48,820 --> 00:45:50,900
[SPEAKER_00] Samo da ga se sjetimo dovoljno često.

1072
00:45:50,900 --> 00:45:53,380
[SPEAKER_01] I možemo zapisati možda te stvari.

1073
00:45:53,380 --> 00:45:55,239
[SPEAKER_01] Imaš li praksu neka zapisivanja

1074
00:45:55,239 --> 00:45:57,320
[SPEAKER_01] nekih svojih misli, ideja,

1075
00:45:57,320 --> 00:45:59,159
[SPEAKER_01] svog zašto, svog cilja?

1076
00:45:59,159 --> 00:46:01,039
[SPEAKER_01] Pa neke ciljeve zapisujem, da.

1077
00:46:01,039 --> 00:46:03,260
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ciljeve zapisujem

1078
00:46:03,260 --> 00:46:04,460
[SPEAKER_00] i to možda ne često.

1079
00:46:04,460 --> 00:46:06,639
[SPEAKER_00] Možda i namirno ne često.

1080
00:46:06,639 --> 00:46:07,940
[SPEAKER_00] Jer želim si dat vrijeme

1081
00:46:07,940 --> 00:46:09,579
[SPEAKER_00] da ih ostvarim.

1082
00:46:09,579 --> 00:46:10,820
[SPEAKER_00] Neke ih zaboravim.

1083
00:46:10,820 --> 00:46:12,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa poste vidim da sam zapisao.

1084
00:46:12,360 --> 00:46:13,360
[SPEAKER_00] Pa sam neke ostvario,

1085
00:46:13,360 --> 00:46:14,039
[SPEAKER_00] neke nisam.

1086
00:46:14,039 --> 00:46:15,800
[SPEAKER_00] Ciljevi koji se zadajem

1087
00:46:15,800 --> 00:46:17,000
[SPEAKER_00] su obično dosta visoki.

1088
00:46:17,000 --> 00:46:19,219
[SPEAKER_00] Jer i tak ih neću ostvariti.

1089
00:46:19,219 --> 00:46:20,900
[SPEAKER_00] Pa ako već neću ostvariti,

1090
00:46:20,900 --> 00:46:21,800
[SPEAKER_00] pa bolje da su visoki

1091
00:46:21,800 --> 00:46:22,900
[SPEAKER_00] pa da dođem blizu.

1092
00:46:23,619 --> 00:46:25,280
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da zapisujem ciljeve

1093
00:46:25,280 --> 00:46:26,559
[SPEAKER_00] više nego svoje misli.

1094
00:46:26,559 --> 00:46:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] Bilo bi dobro da pišem više.

1095
00:46:29,559 --> 00:46:30,539
[SPEAKER_00] To je točno.

1096
00:46:30,539 --> 00:46:32,460
[SPEAKER_00] I želim to promijeniti kod sebe

1097
00:46:32,460 --> 00:46:33,820
[SPEAKER_00] recimo u sljedećih pet godina.

1098
00:46:33,820 --> 00:46:35,559
[SPEAKER_00] Želim više pisat.

1099
00:46:36,659 --> 00:46:38,860
[SPEAKER_00] ne zato što sad imam nešto za reći,

1100
00:46:38,860 --> 00:46:41,360
[SPEAKER_00] nego jednostavno da time složim svoje misli

1101
00:46:41,360 --> 00:46:43,500
[SPEAKER_00] još bolje pa će mi to sigurno pomoći u tome.

1102
00:46:43,500 --> 00:46:46,619
[SPEAKER_00] Radim prezentacije, radim predavanja,

1103
00:46:46,619 --> 00:46:47,519
[SPEAKER_00] ali to je ipak drugo.

1104
00:46:47,519 --> 00:46:49,500
[SPEAKER_00] Pisati svoje misli je nešto

1105
00:46:49,500 --> 00:46:51,239
[SPEAKER_00] ipak drugačije.

1106
00:46:51,239 --> 00:46:52,300
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da može biti korisno

1107
00:46:52,300 --> 00:46:53,380
[SPEAKER_00] i to je jedna od stvari u kojima

1108
00:46:53,380 --> 00:46:54,219
[SPEAKER_00] ja želim biti bolji.

1109
00:46:54,219 --> 00:46:56,019
[SPEAKER_00] Mislim da znam od prilike

1110
00:46:56,019 --> 00:46:57,840
[SPEAKER_00] u kojim stvarima želim biti bolji

1111
00:46:57,840 --> 00:46:59,719
[SPEAKER_00] sad u idućih tri ili pet ili deset godina.

1112
00:47:00,420 --> 00:47:02,239
[SPEAKER_00] I imam neke ciljeve koje želimo stvariti.

1113
00:47:02,239 --> 00:47:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] To sad zvuči možda čudno

1114
00:47:03,559 --> 00:47:05,420
[SPEAKER_00] mojim studentima kad im pričam na prvoj godini

1115
00:47:05,420 --> 00:47:07,219
[SPEAKER_00] i kad ih provociram.

1116
00:47:07,219 --> 00:47:08,119
[SPEAKER_00] U stvari ih provociram

1117
00:47:08,119 --> 00:47:10,099
[SPEAKER_00] i u stvari možda ne provociram

1118
00:47:10,099 --> 00:47:12,219
[SPEAKER_00] nego potičem ih na razmišljenje.

1119
00:47:12,219 --> 00:47:13,280
[SPEAKER_00] To je možda pravilnije.

1120
00:47:13,280 --> 00:47:14,539
[SPEAKER_00] Pozitivna provokacija.

1121
00:47:14,539 --> 00:47:16,500
[SPEAKER_00] Kad mi kaže pa čekaj,

1122
00:47:16,500 --> 00:47:18,400
[SPEAKER_00] kak je moguće da ja danas sam

1123
00:47:18,400 --> 00:47:21,519
[SPEAKER_00] nađemo se u osam u jutro na predavanju.

1124
00:47:21,519 --> 00:47:23,340
[SPEAKER_00] Ja sam taj dan već dvije minute

1125
00:47:23,340 --> 00:47:25,239
[SPEAKER_00] nešto pročitao, nešto naučio.

1126
00:47:25,239 --> 00:47:26,539
[SPEAKER_00] Kak je moguće da sam se ja

1127
00:47:26,539 --> 00:47:28,360
[SPEAKER_00] više usavršavao danas od vas.

1128
00:47:28,360 --> 00:47:31,179
[SPEAKER_00] A vi želite neke stvari raditi kao ja.

1129
00:47:31,179 --> 00:47:32,780
[SPEAKER_00] Ne sve, neke stvari kao ja.

1130
00:47:32,780 --> 00:47:33,960
[SPEAKER_00] I vi ste prva godina faksa.

1131
00:47:33,960 --> 00:47:37,239
[SPEAKER_00] Pa da, to jednostavno mora biti dio tebe

1132
00:47:37,239 --> 00:47:39,260
[SPEAKER_00] da tražiš, ne mora to biti

1133
00:47:39,260 --> 00:47:40,280
[SPEAKER_00] deset sati dnevno,

1134
00:47:40,280 --> 00:47:41,199
[SPEAKER_00] ni ne može biti.

1135
00:47:41,199 --> 00:47:43,739
[SPEAKER_00] Ali da tražiš te sitne vremenske prozore

1136
00:47:43,739 --> 00:47:46,400
[SPEAKER_00] od dvije, tri, pet, deset ili 55 minuta

1137
00:47:46,400 --> 00:47:48,400
[SPEAKER_00] u kojima vidiš nešto novo

1138
00:47:48,400 --> 00:47:50,420
[SPEAKER_00] i znati željan si da bi to dobio.

1139
00:47:50,420 --> 00:47:51,380
[SPEAKER_00] Tako da ta znati želja

1140
00:47:51,380 --> 00:47:53,019
[SPEAKER_00] kod mladih ljudi mislina je nešto

1141
00:47:53,019 --> 00:47:55,780
[SPEAKER_00] što će onda potaknuti i usavršavanje.

1142
00:47:55,780 --> 00:47:58,659
[SPEAKER_00] I onda posljedično i pisanje ciljeva

1143
00:47:58,659 --> 00:48:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] i ostvarivanje tih ciljeva

1144
00:48:00,460 --> 00:48:03,559
[SPEAKER_00] i ambicioznost jer nekako vjerujem

1145
00:48:03,559 --> 00:48:05,599
[SPEAKER_00] da smo, mi smo u sportu uspješna nacija

1146
00:48:05,599 --> 00:48:09,480
[SPEAKER_00] jer vjerujem da smo kompetitivni,

1147
00:48:09,480 --> 00:48:11,219
[SPEAKER_00] nevjerojatno kompetitivni.

1148
00:48:11,219 --> 00:48:13,000
[SPEAKER_00] Sada neko dođe u ovu prostoriju

1149
