[SPEAKER_00] i kaže

1150
00:48:13,500 --> 00:48:16,159
[SPEAKER_00] ja sam bolji od vas u nečemu.

1151
00:48:16,159 --> 00:48:18,199
[SPEAKER_00] Nema šanse, čemu si ti bolji od nas?

1152
00:48:18,199 --> 00:48:20,019
[SPEAKER_00] Ko je to neko?

1153
00:48:20,019 --> 00:48:22,500
[SPEAKER_00] Znači kompetitivni smo, to je nevjerojatno

1154
00:48:22,500 --> 00:48:24,199
