[SPEAKER_00] i ego je pokretač upravo te ambicije

1159
00:48:33,679 --> 00:48:34,639
[SPEAKER_00] i kompetitivnosti,

1160
00:48:34,639 --> 00:48:35,940
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako mislim da smo

1161
00:48:35,940 --> 00:48:38,639
[SPEAKER_00] sposobni stišati ego kada je to potrebno.

1162
00:48:38,639 --> 00:48:40,900
[SPEAKER_00] I ako smo zaista

1163
00:48:40,900 --> 00:48:42,659
[SPEAKER_00] sposobni stišati ego kada je potrebno

1164
