1167
00:48:48,719 --> 00:48:51,139
[SPEAKER_00] Jer ako si dio veće grupe ljudi

1168
00:48:51,139 --> 00:48:52,619
[SPEAKER_00] koja treba raditi zajedno

1169
00:48:52,619 --> 00:48:54,119
[SPEAKER_00] na istom cilju

1170
00:48:54,119 --> 00:48:56,920
[SPEAKER_00] onda taj ego može biti i problem

1171
00:48:56,920 --> 00:48:59,059
[SPEAKER_00] ali ego mora biti prisutan

1172
00:48:59,059 --> 00:49:00,460
[SPEAKER_00] jer bez ega ne može biti uspješan

1173
00:49:00,460 --> 00:49:03,139
[SPEAKER_00] ali ako si sposoban i ti

1174
00:49:03,139 --> 00:49:04,559
[SPEAKER_00] ne samo ti, nego i svi ti ljudi

1175
00:49:04,559 --> 00:49:06,840
[SPEAKER_00] koji žive zajedno, recimo kod nas u reprezentaciji

1176
00:49:06,840 --> 00:49:09,039
[SPEAKER_00] svatko je sposoban stišati svoj ego

1177
00:49:09,039 --> 00:49:12,019
[SPEAKER_00] postaviti se ispod zajedničkog cilja

1178
00:49:12,019 --> 00:49:12,800
[SPEAKER_00] onda imamo šansu.

1179
00:49:12,800 --> 00:49:15,559
[SPEAKER_00] Nama je velika sreća i blagoslov

1180
00:49:15,559 --> 00:49:17,719
[SPEAKER_00] što imamo kapetana koji je takav

1181
00:49:17,719 --> 00:49:19,800
[SPEAKER_00] da je spreman stišati svoj ego

1182
00:49:19,800 --> 00:49:23,760
[SPEAKER_00] a to je jedan od najkompetitivnijih likova

1183
00:49:23,760 --> 00:49:25,179
[SPEAKER_00] koje ja poznajem

1184
00:49:25,179 --> 00:49:26,500
[SPEAKER_00] a sposoban stišati svoj ego.

1185
00:49:26,500 --> 00:49:28,260
[SPEAKER_00] Imamo izbornika koji je takav

1186
00:49:28,260 --> 00:49:29,559
[SPEAKER_00] da je sposoban stišati svoj ego

1187
00:49:29,559 --> 00:49:30,340
[SPEAKER_00] kada je potrebno

1188
