1193
00:49:38,679 --> 00:49:39,380
[SPEAKER_00] težak dres.

1194
00:49:39,380 --> 00:49:41,940
[SPEAKER_00] Pa mislim da, težak je ne samo zbog očekivanja

1195
00:49:41,940 --> 00:49:43,579
