1196
00:49:43,579 --> 00:49:46,500
[SPEAKER_00] nego je težak jer podrazumijeva neke standarde.

1197
00:49:46,500 --> 00:49:47,880
[SPEAKER_00] Standardi su ti.

1198
00:49:47,880 --> 00:49:49,280
[SPEAKER_00] Moraš biti kompetitivan,

1199
00:49:49,280 --> 00:49:51,559
[SPEAKER_00] moraš imat angažman svaki dan

1200
00:49:51,559 --> 00:49:52,760
[SPEAKER_00] na treningu maksimalan,

1201
00:49:52,760 --> 00:49:55,099
[SPEAKER_00] moraš brinuti o tijelu van terena

1202
00:49:55,099 --> 00:49:57,280
[SPEAKER_00] ali isto tako moraš biti sposoban

1203
00:49:57,280 --> 00:49:58,019
[SPEAKER_00] stišati svoj ego

1204
