1208
00:50:05,199 --> 00:50:06,440
[SPEAKER_00] i svake firme

1209
00:50:06,440 --> 00:50:08,639
[SPEAKER_00] pa i svake obitelji vjerojatno

1210
00:50:08,639 --> 00:50:10,860
[SPEAKER_00] u kojoj isto tako bi trebalo

1211
