[SPEAKER_00] imati neke standarde

1212
00:50:12,519 --> 00:50:14,400
[SPEAKER_00] koje živimo, koje ne moramo pisati

1213
00:50:14,400 --> 00:50:15,679
[SPEAKER_00] nego ih živimo.

1214
00:50:15,679 --> 00:50:18,360
[SPEAKER_01] E sad si mi dao tu sto stvari

1215
00:50:18,360 --> 00:50:19,320
[SPEAKER_01] koje te hoću pitati.

1216
00:50:19,320 --> 00:50:21,480
[SPEAKER_01] Pa krenimo redom.

1217
00:50:21,480 --> 00:50:22,579
[SPEAKER_01] Drago mi je da si spomenuo

1218
00:50:22,579 --> 00:50:23,920
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo taj vrkonski sport

1219
00:50:23,920 --> 00:50:25,300
[SPEAKER_01] jer ljudi često misle

1220
00:50:25,300 --> 00:50:26,300
[SPEAKER_01] da nemaju veze s tim.

1221
00:50:26,300 --> 00:50:27,380
[SPEAKER_01] Da su to ljudi koji imaju

1222
00:50:27,380 --> 00:50:30,019
[SPEAKER_01] nadmoćne nekakve vještine

1223
00:50:30,019 --> 00:50:32,199
[SPEAKER_01] koji su jednostavno drugačiji od drugih

1224
00:50:32,199 --> 00:50:33,559
[SPEAKER_01] koji su jako talentirani

1225
00:50:33,559 --> 00:50:34,980
[SPEAKER_01] zbog toga su tu di jesu.

1226
00:50:34,980 --> 00:50:36,320
[SPEAKER_01] No evo,

1227
00:50:36,320 --> 00:50:38,159
[SPEAKER_01] s obzirom da se i sama bavim

1228
00:50:38,159 --> 00:50:39,800
[SPEAKER_01] i živim u tom sportu

1229
00:50:39,800 --> 00:50:40,820
[SPEAKER_01] već 20 godina

1230
00:50:40,820 --> 00:50:42,659
[SPEAKER_01] znam da to ni baš uvijek tako.

1231
00:50:42,659 --> 00:50:44,159
[SPEAKER_01] Spominješ organizaciju,

1232
00:50:44,159 --> 00:50:45,260
[SPEAKER_01] odmicanje od ega,

1233
00:50:45,260 --> 00:50:47,000
[SPEAKER_01] kompetitivnost,

1234
00:50:47,000 --> 00:50:47,599
[SPEAKER_01] angažman,

1235
00:50:47,599 --> 00:50:48,559
[SPEAKER_01] brigu o tijelu,

1236
