1237
00:50:49,699 --> 00:50:50,780
[SPEAKER_01] zrelost.

1238
00:50:50,780 --> 00:50:52,739
[SPEAKER_01] Sad mi zvoni ta riješ zrelost

1239
00:50:52,739 --> 00:50:53,239
[SPEAKER_01] s kojoj je,

1240
00:50:53,239 --> 00:50:54,539
[SPEAKER_01] nedavno smo čuli to

1241
00:50:54,539 --> 00:50:55,480
[SPEAKER_01] zapravo od doktora

1242
00:50:55,480 --> 00:50:56,860
[SPEAKER_01] Pere Kuterovca,

1243
00:50:56,860 --> 00:50:58,780
