[SPEAKER_01] s tim egom.

1247
00:51:03,519 --> 00:51:05,960
[SPEAKER_01] Ajmo se malo tu zadržati

1248
00:51:05,960 --> 00:51:07,719
[SPEAKER_01] i probaj nam opisati

1249
00:51:07,719 --> 00:51:09,699
[SPEAKER_01] kako u jednoj takvoj organizaciji,

1250
00:51:09,699 --> 00:51:11,119
[SPEAKER_01] što se događa,

1251
00:51:11,119 --> 00:51:12,780
[SPEAKER_01] koliko ljudi zapravo

1252
00:51:12,780 --> 00:51:14,639
[SPEAKER_01] naglašavaju tu osobnu odgovornost

1253
00:51:14,639 --> 00:51:15,320
[SPEAKER_01] i samim tim,

1254
00:51:15,320 --> 00:51:17,440
[SPEAKER_01] taj tim čine uspješnim,

1255
00:51:17,440 --> 00:51:18,800
[SPEAKER_01] naša repka je stvarno jedna

1256
